    • RMIConnectionHandler

      public RMIConnectionHandler(UI userInterface) throws Exception
      This constructor creates a new RMIConnectionHandler. Initializes the fields and set null the gameServerActions (game is not started). After that, it tries to connect to the rmi main server and created 2 threads with a consumer fot the command queues.

    • sendToMainServer

      public boolean sendToMainServer(MainCommand mainCommand)
      This method sends a main command to the main server. If the command is a ConnectionCommand, it connects to the server calling connectToMain and waits for the user info. If the command is a ReconnectionCommand, it creates a new RMIMainView and calls the reconnect method and waits for the user info. In any other case, it sends the command to the server.
      Specified by:
      sendToMainServer in class ConnectionHandler
      Parameters:
      mainCommand - the command to be sent
      Returns:
      true if the command is sent, false otherwise
